'''Alton Lannister''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by guest star [[Karl Davies]] and debuts in &quot;[[The North Remembers]].&quot; Ser Alton Lannister is a young [[knight]] from a [[cadet branch]] of [[House Lannister]] and a captive of the [[The North|Northern]] armies alongside his cousin, Ser [[Jaime Lannister]]. He is sent to deliver [[Robb Stark]]'s peace terms to [[King's Landing]], and he is killed by Jaime Lannister inside a prison cell at Robb Stark's camp.
